<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>About &mdash; Detroit Bridal Shower</title>
<link rel="icon" href="../assets/images/bridalshowerpic.jpg">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,500;1,600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root { --ivory:#f4f1ea; --cream:#faf8f3; --sage:#494e46; --sage-dark:#383c36; --gold:#b3925a; --gold-soft:#f3ead9;
    --ink:#2e2e29; --soft:#6d6d64; --line:#e7e2d8; --serif:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif; --sans:'Jost','Segoe UI',sans-serif; }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { background:var(--ivory); font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink); }
  a { text-decoration:none; }
  .n-nav { position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50; background:rgba(244,241,234,.92); backdrop-filter:blur(10px); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  .n-nav-in { max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; padding:14px 22px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:26px; }
  .n-brand { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
  .n-brand img { width:44px; height:44px; object-fit:contain; background:#fff; border-radius:50%; padding:4px; border:1px solid var(--line); }
  .n-brand span { font-family:var(--serif); font-weight:600; font-size:17px; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--sage-dark); line-height:1.2; }
  .n-links { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:26px; margin-left:auto; }
  .n-links a { font-size:13.5px; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--sage); }
  .n-links a:hover { color:var(--gold); }
  .n-cta { background:var(--gold); color:#fff !important; border-radius:999px; padding:11px 24px; }
  @media (max-width:820px){ .n-links a:not(.n-cta){ display:none; } }
  .hero { text-align:center; padding:66px 20px 26px; }
  .hero img { width:120px; margin:0 auto 16px; display:block; }
  .kicker { font-size:12px; letter-spacing:5px; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); font-weight:500; }
  .hero h1 { font-family:var(--serif); font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(36px,5.5vw,52px); color:var(--sage-dark); margin:14px 0 8px; line-height:1.15; }
  .hero h1 em { font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); }
  .wrap { max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; padding:14px 22px 40px; }
  .lede { font-family:var(--serif); font-size:22px; color:var(--soft); line-height:1.65; text-align:center; }
  .divider { width:54px; height:1px; background:#d9c9a6; margin:36px auto; }
  .block h2 { font-family:var(--serif); font-weight:600; font-size:27px; color:var(--sage-dark); margin-bottom:12px; text-align:center; }
  .block p { font-family:var(--serif); font-size:19px; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .block a { color:var(--gold); }
  .cta-band { background:var(--cream); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); text-align:center; padding:52px 20px; }
  .cta-band h2 { font-family:var(--serif); font-style:italic; font-weight:500; font-size:30px; color:var(--sage); margin-bottom:22px; }
  .btn { display:inline-block; border-radius:999px; padding:14px 32px; font-size:14.5px; letter-spacing:.06em; margin:0 6px 10px; }
  .btn-gold { background:var(--gold); color:#fff !important; }
  .btn-line { border:1px solid var(--sage); color:var(--sage) !important; }
  .foot { text-align:center; padding:34px 20px 40px; font-weight:300; font-size:12.5px; color:var(--soft); line-height:1.9; }
  .foot a { color:var(--gold); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="n-nav"><div class="n-nav-in">
  <a class="n-brand" href="/"><img src="../assets/images/bridalshowerpic.jpg" alt=""><span>Detroit<br>Bridal Shower</span></a>
  <div class="n-links">
    <a href="/give">Give a Gift</a>
    <a href="/contributors">With Gratitude</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    <a class="n-cta" href="/#services">Add a Couple</a>
  </div>
</div></div>

<div class="hero">
  <img src="../assets/images/bridalshowerpic.jpg" alt="Detroit Bridal Shower">
  <div class="kicker">Our story</div>
  <h1>Built by a community,<br><em>for every new couple</em></h1>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <p class="lede">For years, the women of our Detroit community have come together around a simple idea: no chosson and kallah should begin married life with an empty home.</p>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="block">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>When a couple gets engaged, friends and family from across the community each give toward their bridal shower. The funds are pooled and spent thoughtfully on the essentials &mdash; kitchenware, linens, appliances, the cholent pot &mdash; everything a new home needs from day one.</p>
    <p>With everything purchased together, every dollar is used wisely, and the new couple can focus on what matters: building a bayis ne'eman b'Yisroel.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="block">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>Anyone can <a href="/#services">add a newly engaged couple</a> to the list. Once confirmed, the community is notified, and everyone can <a href="/give">give toward the shower</a> in under a minute. Every contributor is honored on our <a href="/contributors">With Gratitude</a> page &mdash; because every gift, no matter the size, builds a home.</p>
    <p>Prefer to shop yourself? Our <a onclick="window.open('../assets/images/shoppingGuide.pdf','_blank')" style="cursor:pointer;">shopping guide</a> lays out everything a new household needs.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div class="block">
    <h2>A community project</h2>
    <p>The Detroit Bridal Shower Project is a 501(c)(4) not-for-profit organization, run entirely by volunteers. Every simcha we celebrate is made possible by this community's generosity &mdash; thank you, Detroit.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cta-band">
  <h2>Share in the next simcha</h2>
  <a class="btn btn-gold" href="/#services">Add a Couple</a>
  <a class="btn btn-line" href="/give">Give a Gift</a>
</div>

<div class="foot">
  17322 Goldwin Drive &bull; Southfield, MI 48075 &bull; <a href="tel:2485147963">248-514-7963</a><br>
  <a href="mailto:bridalshower@detroitbridalshower.org">bridalshower@detroitbridalshower.org</a><br>
  &copy; Detroit Bridal Shower Project &middot; 501(c)(4) not-for-profit
</div>
</body>
</html>
